author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3403 Cannot convert 'this.content' to object in Opera
First set the onload handler and then update the iframe's location.
Additionally bind onload to this so it is possible to get a reference to this.content (the iframe).

author: mgrigorov

First set the onload handler for the iframe then update its location.
Additionally bind onload to 'this' so it is possible to get a reference to the 'content' (the iframe)
